Package: cultevo
Title: Tools, Measures and Statistical Tests for Cultural Evolution
Version: 1.0.2
Date: 2018-04-24
Authors@R: person("Kevin Stadler", role=c("aut", "cre"),
        email="a00425926@unet.univie.ac.at")
Description: Provides tools for measuring the compositionality of
        signalling systems (in particular the information-theoretic
        measure due to Spike (2016) <http://hdl.handle.net/1842/25930>
        and the Mantel test for distance matrix correlation (after
        Dietz 1983) <doi:10.1093/sysbio/32.1.21>), functions for
        computing string and meaning distance matrices as well as an
        implementation of the Page test for monotonicity of ranks (Page
        1963) <doi:10.1080/01621459.1963.10500843> with exact p-values
        up to k = 22.
URL: https://kevinstadler.github.io/cultevo/
